Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:36.02,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(109,373)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,2060,2420)}Táo Qiān\NStyled: "Gōngzǔ"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Please rest assured, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:49.10,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(555,358)\fade(255,0,255,0,200,1800,2160)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: "Mèngdé"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Táo Qiān's men have murdered my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He will be avenged!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiàhóu Dūn will lead the vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.27,0:00:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone dares to aid the Xú-province...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Show no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:00:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,After Cáo Cāo failed to defeat Dǒng Zhuó,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,he garrisoned his forces at Shāndōng
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and ordered his men to\N leave for Lángyá Commandery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,to pick up his father and his household and bring them back to Shāndōng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.55,0:01:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Along the way in Xú-Province, Táo Qiān,\Nseeking to become allies with Cáo Cāo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,sent his subordinate, Zhāng Kǎi, \Nto escort his father along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But Zhāng Kǎi wanted to seize his wealth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and so, en route, he murdered his entire household.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo, furious from this, \Nled his soldiers to annihilate the Xú-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:56.06,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,355)\fade(255,0,255,0,450,1660,1950)}Chén Gōng\NStyled: "Gōngtái"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could save the people of Xú-Province,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I would hand over it's provincial seal to Cáo Cāo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and let him execute me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, you can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:20.02,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(110,350)\fade(255,0,255,0,400,4750,5100)}Mí Zhú\NStyled: "Zizhòng"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, you have long governed the Xú-Province! The people love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But Cáo's army is mighty!\N We can't beat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But he hasn't breached the walls of the Xú-Province's capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You and the people need to unite!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me exit the city! I will ask \NKǒng Róng for reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But if they don't arrive soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the city will have been breached!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'Father of Lord Cáo, Sōng.'{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, there's someone called Chén Gōng who wishes to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't see anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Chén Gōng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Which Chén Gōng?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The magistrate who released you in Zhōngmu county,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That Chén Gōng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Call him in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngtái, have you been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am doing fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder now, Gōngtái, where have you been since we last met?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I am stationed in Dōng Commandery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good post you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, you jest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I always knew you and\Nthat Táo Qiān were good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to beg for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly the reason why I have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, to avenge your esteemed father, you sent an army to siege Xú-Province,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but Táo Qiān is a benevolent lord and not one to abandon justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father's death was due to Zhāng Kǎi, not Táo Qiān's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, what animosity do you have with the people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet wherever you march...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're doing is a massacre!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chén Gōng, back then you abandoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What right do you have to talk to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Táo Qiān murdered my entire family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I vowed to rip out his gall \Nand cut out his heart for vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:20.72,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(155,345)}Kǒng Róng\NStyled: "Wénjǔ"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Táo Gōngzǔ can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a plan to repel the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to introduce you to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call over Lord Liú!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:50.34,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(205,355)\fade(255,0,255,0,390,6050,6380)}Liú Bèi\NStyled: "Xuándé"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Mí, I've long known about the situation in the Xú-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Táo Gōngzǔ is a benevolent lord.\NHe should not suffer for other's guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sir, during the Eighteen Lord's expedition against Dǒng Zhuó,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,have you heard of Sir Liú, Guān, and Zhāng, who fought Lǚ Bù at the Hǔláo Pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:04.11,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(598,365)}Guān Yǔ\NStyled: "Yúnchǎng"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Liú is a true champion of our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If he can come aid \Nthe Xú-Province, he can lift the siege.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Sir, I've long known about\Nyour righteousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}and your ability to save those in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Now the Xú-Province stands alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}their people in peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Please save us from this peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Lord Xuándé, you are a scion of the Imperial House,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Now Cáo Cāo attacks and subjugates the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Why not come to their rescue?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I wouldn't dare refuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}but I lack the troops to take drastic actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Sir, I want to save Táo Gōngzǔ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}not just for our friendship,\Nbut also for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Sir, how could you not uphold justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Administrator Kǒng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:09:00.42,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(108,355)\fade(255,0,255,0,490,4820,5220)}Zhāng Fēi\NStyled: "Yìdé"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, please give us troops
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and let me go to Gōngsūn Zàn to borrow 35,000 troops. I will be back afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lucky to have met a hero like yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Tomorrow, I will provide you with the troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you won't go back on your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Sir, who do you think I am?\NThe sages have said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}"Without trust cannot a man stand."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Whether I bring back soldiers or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I will come back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right, Liú Xuándé truly is a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,With Lord Xuándé here, the Xú-Province is saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the city gates!\NOpen the gates for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liú arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, I was afraid that you had no provisions left
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and wouldn't hold out for long,\N so I forced my way in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to strategize a way to make the enemy retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To have you come to our rescue,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, it's a sign for mercy\N for the people of the Xú-Province!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mí Zhú.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the Seal of the Xú-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, what is this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}The nation is in great disorder, and the imperium lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Sir, you are a scion of the Hàn,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}able to support the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I'm but an old man now, too feeble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I would gladly gift you the Xú-Province!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}The words you thus spoke have humbled me greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Though I am of the Hàn dynasty, \NI'm of only humble merits and virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I only hold a lowly office at Píngyuán.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I am here only for the common good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Sir, the words you spoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Does sire suspect me to desire annexing the Xú-Province?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}If I harbored such thoughts, \Nmay heavens abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My words are sincere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will submit a memorial to the \Nimperial court of my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, sir, please accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, right now our foes are besieging our gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Our priority should be to repel them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, what Lord Liú spoke is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! I will write to Cáo Cāo\N to urge his retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If he refuses, then we will strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does Liú Bèi think he is,\N asking me to retreat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocking me between the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill the messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:50.34,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(150,340)\fade(255,0,255,0,600,3755,4100)}Guō Jiā \NStyled: "Fèngxiào"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, Liú Bèi has come afar, \Nyet negotiates before using force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord should reply with courtesy, lower his guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,then assault the city walls! The city will fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! An urgent report for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Report! Lǚ Bù followed Chén Gōng's plan\Nand captured Shāndōng!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the reports!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Rén has reported,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}"Recently, Chén Gōng of Dōng County\Njoined Zhāng Miǎo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}"and advised Lǚ Bù to seize Shāndōng and advance into Púyáng."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}"We only have Juànchéng, Dōng'ā, and Fàn County left, thanks to Xún Yù and others' last ditch effort."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}"The rest were taken by Lǚ Bù!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Cáo Rén couldn't win them back,\Nso he requested aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}After that, Lǚ Bù was forced by Lǐ Jué and Guō Sì to leave Cháng'ān.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}He joined Yuán Shù,\Nand then joined Yuán Shào.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}He left him and then Zhāng Yáng\Nto join Zhāng Miǎo like a cur!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Lǚ Bù is a reckless fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Who would've thought, that trivial\N Chén Gōng could be able to do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}just for my refusal over the Xú-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}My Lord, Shāndōng is lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}We have no home to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}The only way back is to retake our lost lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}What the General has spoke is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}The vengeance against Xú-Province must be delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}It's better to do Liú Bèi a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}and withdraw to retake Shāndōng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liú arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liú, your letter saved us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, you are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only a small favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I have prepared light wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A banquet for all you loyal and righteous heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I have something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you gentlemen to heed it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I am old and ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My two sons are incapable of administering the province.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuándé is of the imperial clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With his virtue and talent, he can lead the Xú-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I am willing to retire and heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kǒng Wénjǔ wanted me to save the Xú-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a just act. I'm not here to seize the Xú-Province,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,lest I be known as corrupt and disloyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hàn Empire is declining and the realm is in anarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to rebuild.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the Xú-Province is rich, \Nwith tens of thousands households.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liú, you are fit to lead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place where you can lead by example.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you mustn't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:31.86,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(596,368)\fade(255,0,255,0,415,4345,4820)}Chén Dēng\NStyled: "Yuánlóng"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Táo is constantly ill \Nand mustn't manage affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you have to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, Yuán Gōnglù's clan has long served as the Three Excellencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Those within the four seas look up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And he resides at Shòuchūn, near here.\NWhy not let him have the Xú-Province?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuán Shù is but a a corpse in a tomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuándé, this is a chance sent by the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you refuse it,\Nthen you will regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I can't accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuándé, if you refuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, you should accept Lord Táo's offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, you are fit to lead the Xú-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! It's not like we are forcing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to resign,\Nso refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to entice me to treachery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, I dare not accept your offer of Xú-Province!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuándé, if you are unwilling to do so,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a small city near here, called Xiǎopèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You may garrison there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, would you please garrison there\Nfor some time to protect the Xú-Province?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Xuándé has no need to decline, surely?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can all rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:42.25,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(128,355)}Lǚ Bù\NStyled: "Fèngxiān"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǚ Bù!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We had no quarrel between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you steal my territory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a share of the Empire's land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can you seize the Xú-Province,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,yet I cannot take Shāndōng?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched Lǚ Bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is willing to take down Lǚ Bu?! Kill that arrogance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Chén Gōng! A baseborn magistrate like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you dare work with a tiger\N and encourage his troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You will die for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo rushed back to \NShāndōng to fight with Lǚ Bù.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Chén Gōng kept on presenting plans to make Cáo Cāo lose one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Cáo Cāo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That man riding a yellow horse!\NThat's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, go! My Lord, go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Battle of Púyáng, \NCáo Cāo almost lost his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the same year that locusts started to swarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo, with his provisions empty due to this,\Nhad to retreat to Ju'àn-City.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǚ Bù also retreated and fortified inside Púyáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus, the conflict ceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo's army has left...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be due to Lǚ Bù's attack on Shāndōng...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.35,0:23:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They may have retreated, \Nbut they will return by spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't help but to recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...the massacre Cáo's army did in the Xú-Province...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, you must not worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chén Dēng already went to Xiǎopèi\Nto summon Lord Liú here a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Xú-Province... Do you think...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, you tried to resign twice to Xuándé.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, you were still healthy enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.00,0:23:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so Lord Xuándé wouldn't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.26,0:23:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you are ill, \Nhe must not be able to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.70,0:24:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.72,0:24:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.66,0:24:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, how has your condition gotten to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.27,0:24:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise... Rise... Bring seating...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.27,0:24:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, you must rest assured. Don't-
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.91,0:25:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know... Once Cáo Cāo takes revenge on Lǚ Bù...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.78,0:25:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...He will come for us too...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.92,0:25:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,... The Xú-Province... Is at crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.13,0:25:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sir... Take pity on the poor people!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.77,0:25:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Preserve this city for Hàn Empire's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.74,0:25:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.28,0:25:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, you have two sons. \NWhy not let them inherit this duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.92,0:25:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of my sons have the skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.66,0:25:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After I die... I hope you will tutor them...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.79,0:25:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But never let them into political affairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.34,0:26:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I be prepared\Nfor this great responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.98,0:26:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me recommend one person... That can assist you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.58,0:26:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He is called Sūn Qián, of Běihǎi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.39,0:26:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Zizhòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.72,0:26:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.03,0:26:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liú is a champion of the times...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.97,0:26:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope... you will serve him well...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.12,0:26:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.66,0:26:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.93,0:27:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Order all in Xú-Province to attend the mourning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.05,0:27:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.75,0:27:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? That bastard Táo Qiān has died?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.22,0:27:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That Liú Bèi took over Xú-Province with no effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.00,0:27:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He's pushing his luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.46,0:27:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill Liú Bèi first,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.86,0:27:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,then dig out and flay that Táo Qiān's corpse, and avenge my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.90,0:27:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, what is your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.54,0:27:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.74,0:27:39.18,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(125,360)\fade(255,0,255,0,415,2945,3420)}Xún Yù\NStyled: "Wénruò"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.04,0:27:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, do not send an army to the Xú-Province this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.31,0:27:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.47,0:27:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Of old, Hàn Gāozǔ guarded Guānzhōng, and Hàn Guāngwǔ occupied Hénèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.40,0:27:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Both of them were deep-rooted and had firm foundations.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.60,0:27:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}It was enough for them to advance and to retreat whilst having a strong base.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.33,0:27:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}That was how they realized their great undertaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.62,0:28:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}If you take the Xú-Province today with
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.66,0:28:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}too many soldiers left, it will be hard to maintain;
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.82,0:28:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}too few soldiers left, then Lǚ Bù will take advantage and seize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.96,0:28:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}If you lose Shāndōng \Nand fail to take the Xú-Province,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.63,0:28:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}then where would sire retreat?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.01,0:28:25.55,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Even if I let go of my grudge,\NI will still obtain the Xú-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.00,0:28:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Rén and Xiàhóu Dūn!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.61,0:28:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.39,0:28:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You two guard Ju'ànchéng!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.00,0:28:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.03,0:28:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eliminate Lǚ Bù first, remove all potential obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.56,0:28:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.07,0:29:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Rally the remnants of our army!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.27,0:29:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will end that bastard Cáo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.74,0:29:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,General, Cáo's army is powerful. \NYou cannot compete with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.58,0:29:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find shelter first, \Nand then can we take revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.71,0:29:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you told me to take Shāndōng, you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.05,0:29:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cáo Cāo is nothing to be afraid of!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.25,0:29:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngtái, if I ally with Yuán Shào again.\NHow does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.75,0:30:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You've left Yuán Shào before.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.41,0:30:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,General, your arrogance cost us nearly all our soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.89,0:30:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you attempt to join him again,\NI fear there is no room.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.83,0:30:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can first send scouts to the Jì-Province,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.23,0:30:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if Yuán Shào won't tolerate us, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.78,0:30:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps joining with Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.57,0:30:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.25,0:30:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to save the Xú-Province\N but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.36,0:30:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǚ Bù is a beast! He mustn't be taken in!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.02,0:30:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He will bring harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.30,0:31:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for Lǚ Bù's attack at Shāndōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.68,0:31:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we wouldn't have rescued Xú-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.02,0:31:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, he came to me in need.\N How could I let him down?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.55,0:31:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you are too kind. Even so, be vigilant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.69,0:31:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yide, you will come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.97,0:31:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring my horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.00,0:31:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.36,0:32:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}After I plotted with {\i1}the Minister over the Masses{\i0},\NWáng, to kill Dǒng Zhuō,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.26,0:32:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}we were attacked by Lǐ Jué and Guō Sì, so I wandered east.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.96,0:32:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Many of the warlords didn't give me shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.13,0:32:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Today, I came here to join you.\NWe'll achieve great things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.70,0:32:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.73,0:32:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}When Cáo Cāo came to attack the Xú-Province,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.50,0:32:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}thanks to your capturing of Shāndōng, \Nhelped lift the siege on the Xú-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.28,0:32:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Now with Lord Táo's passing, and no one left to govern the Xú-Province,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.15,0:32:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I stepped up to manage the provincial affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.11,0:32:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Fortunately,with your presence, I can step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.62,0:33:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I am only a warrior,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.91,0:33:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}How could I administer a province?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.44,0:33:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}General, please accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.44,0:33:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}As is it said,\N"a strong guest does not oppress the owner."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.57,0:33:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Please don't doubt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.02,0:33:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.02,0:33:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}See, when I captured Shāndōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.31,0:33:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I hoped to establish a base to achieve my cause
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.22,0:34:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}but fell to that treacherous Cáo's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.42,0:34:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}My army suffered, losing most of its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.57,0:34:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Now that you have taken me in,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.15,0:34:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}in the midst of grim circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.46,0:34:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I am grateful and indebted \Nto sire's righteousness and compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.19,0:34:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! Bring them out to pay respects to Our Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.36,0:34:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My family now has a place to live, \Nthanks to Lord Liú's generosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.87,0:34:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You must bow down to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.07,0:34:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.41,0:34:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, there is no need to be humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.88,0:35:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My Elder Brother is kin of the Hàn!\NWho do you think you are!?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.45,0:35:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dare claim him as your brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.25,0:35:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over here! Let me have at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.75,0:35:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even my Elder Brother\N refused to accept the seal many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.26,0:35:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet why should a cur like you deserve the Xú-Province!?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.99,0:35:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My younger brother is just raving. Please don't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.69,0:35:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you for receiving me over refusal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.76,0:35:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But if since your younger brother\Nwon't tolerate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.73,0:35:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I will seek refuge elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.27,0:35:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.74,0:36:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go, then it's my great mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.08,0:36:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My younger brother was just raving,\NI'll make him apologize to you another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.16,0:36:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Better I just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.33,0:36:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a place called Xiǎopèi, where you can stock up on soldiers and provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.81,0:36:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,General, if you don't mind, \Nyou may garrison your men there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.11,0:36:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good military supplies should\N make up for this offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.68,0:36:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,General, if...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.39,0:36:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.34,0:37:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.49,0:37:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the Son of Heaven\N moved the capital to Luòyáng,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.69,0:37:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}news of him hounded by Lǐ and Guō \Npassed to Shāndōng,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.27,0:37:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shocking Cáo Cāo and all officers, who had only been planning an assault on Xú-Province.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.14,0:37:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.34,0:37:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Though Liú Bèi took in Lǚ Bù, I think plans for the Xú-Province ought to be delayed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.92,0:37:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,now that the Emperor has moved to Luòyáng,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.59,0:38:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a matter of great \Nimportance that we need to consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.77,0:38:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Of old, Duke Wén of Jìn reinstated King Xiāng of Zhōu,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.77,0:38:13.43,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: When King Xiāng of Zhōu was deposed by his brother. \NDuke Wén of Jìn used his power to reinstate the deposed King.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.17,0:38:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}all the warlords accepted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.43,0:38:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}When Emperor Gāozǔ of Hàn mourned over Emperor Yì,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.58,0:38:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}the whole world swore allegiance to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.43,0:38:18.60,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Yì was the Emperor of Chǔ, formerly King Huai II.\NHe was murdered by Xiàng Yǔ, Gāozǔ's rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.16,0:38:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Now the Son of Heaven has lost his power and fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.05,0:38:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}My sir, if you were to call upon under a righteous cause,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.98,0:38:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}to receive the Emperor and the people's will,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.13,0:38:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}would be to re-establish the heavenly order.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.35,0:38:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}If you don't act now, then others will act first!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.22,0:38:43.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}The Emperor loses his power
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.90,0:38:46.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}if called upon under a righteous cause
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.33,0:38:48.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}to receive the Emperor and the people's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.60,0:38:50.62,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}It would be to re-establish the heavenly order.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.00,0:38:55.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}If I don't act now, then others will act first!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.68,0:39:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Son of Heaven thus orders Cáo Cāo to enter the imperial court and assist the royal family!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.75,0:39:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo, accept this order!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.21,0:39:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your minister, Cáo Cāo, accepts!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.92,0:39:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.19,0:39:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.40,0:39:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,General, spare me!\NPlease spare me for this offense!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.66,0:40:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I received the nation's grace, of which I shall repay!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.60,0:40:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Under orders I shall escort the Emperor to the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.80,0:40:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}for the spirit of the nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.12,0:40:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I call upon righteous soldiers against all adversity!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.10,0:40:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}We shall march as legion invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.92,0:40:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the Emperor! Onward to Luòyáng! March!
